[quote][color=#ffffff][size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size][/color][/quote]Download manually and extract the slot file to your Documents/My Games/Skyrim/CME_save
Start Skyrim and go into the character creation menu. Load slot number, Slot 1
(You can rename [b]ONLY[/b] the number to change the slot) 
[quote][color=#ffffff][size=4][b]Permissions[/b][/size][/color][/quote][size=3]DO NOT make a follower of this preset without my permission![/size]
